    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hide and Sheep is a 2-10 player online multiplayer social-deduction party game. Players need to blend in with the AI sheep, identify the other real players, and strike before they do!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Blending In</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't let other players detect you! Blend in by mimicking AI sheep—move, graze, look around and act exactly like them. When possible, use the environment to conceal yourself from others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207340/extras/c08f315d179cc746a1a461213ac19a5b.poster.avif?t=1764403586\" width=616 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207340/extras/c08f315d179cc746a1a461213ac19a5b.webm?t=1764403586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207340/extras/c08f315d179cc746a1a461213ac19a5b.mp4?t=1764403586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hunt or Be Hunted</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep an eye out for weird behaviour, then keep track of their ear tag number. When the time is right, eliminate them! Just be cautious, every attack risks blowing your cover! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207340/extras/fb9583aea7c56ea635ff61b0afaf1b3d.poster.avif?t=1764403586\" width=616 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207340/extras/fb9583aea7c56ea635ff61b0afaf1b3d.webm?t=1764403586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207340/extras/fb9583aea7c56ea635ff61b0afaf1b3d.mp4?t=1764403586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mushrooms</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each game features a new set of mushrooms — but watch out, their colours change every time! Discover their effects by observing sheep… or by daring to eat them yourself! Mushrooms can help, hinder, or often do both at once. Learn their secrets, then use them wisely to win!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207340/extras/18e15f257ce54ad03a94ec7e470fe0bd.poster.avif?t=1764403586\" width=616 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207340/extras/18e15f257ce54ad03a94ec7e470fe0bd.webm?t=1764403586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207340/extras/18e15f257ce54ad03a94ec7e470fe0bd.mp4?t=1764403586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Maps</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each map drops you into a distinct environment—like a forest, farm or meadow—with its own features and cover. You’ll need to adapt  and use the terrain to your advantage.</p>",
